âœ… What SonarQube Actually Checks

SonarQube does three main things:

Category	What It Checks	Examples
Style / Formatting	PEP8, naming, unused imports	flake8, pycodestyle
Complexity + Maintainability	Cognitive complexity, too many params, duplicate code	radon, jellyfish, wily
Security / Vulnerability Scans	Insecure functions, injection risks	bandit, semgrep
ğŸ¥‡ If you want a Ruff-like all-in-one, the closest SonarQube-like local alternative is:
